WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Everyone ultimately wanted to have a comfortable life. So we organized the 

00:08.000 --> 00:17.000
people into food collectors, exchanged labour with people in the area, and 

00:17.000 --> 00:26.000
managed to get some food. It was not easy. And it was 

00:26.000 --> 00:35.000
still a hard life. But it was considerably better than under the 

00:35.000 --> 00:44.000
gatherer. 

